<p>A single letter that is also a numeral defaults to alphabetic:</p>
<ol start="3" type="a">
<li>third by letter</li>
<li>fourth by letter</li>
</ol>
<p>The letter i alone is read as a roman numeral:</p>
<ol type="i">
<li>one</li>
<li>two</li>
</ol>
